00:16:57,289 --> 00:17:00,660
Aku di sini bukah hanya untuk sementara lagi.

183
00:17:01,319 --> 00:17:03,660
Jika semua staf hotel mengetahuinya,

184
00:17:04,029 --> 00:17:05,390
